<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Grid Bot - Fehler</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0f172a;
            --error-color: #ef4444;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --accent-color: #f97316;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1), transparent 50%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .error-card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            animation: shake 0.5s cubic-bezier(.36,.07,.19,.97) both;
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            10%, 90% { transform: translate3d(-1px, 0, 0); }
            20%, 80% { transform: translate3d(2px, 0, 0); }
            30%, 50%, 70% { transform: translate3d(-4px, 0, 0); }
            40%, 60% { transform: translate3d(4px, 0, 0); }
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            display: block;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--error-color);
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 13px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }

        .made-by {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-card">
            <span class="icon">🚫</span>
            <h1>Nicht berechtigt</h1>
            <p>Du hast keine Berechtigung, auf dieses Dashboard zuzugreifen. Nur der Besitzer des Bots kann diese Seite anzeigen.</p>
            
            <a href="/logout" class="btn-home">Zurück zum Login</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        made by <span class="made-by">MaxiFaxiPaxi</span>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
